Interface IBasePresenter<V extends IBaseView>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - The view.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasePresenter, EngineersPresenter, MainPresenter, SchedulesPresenter

    public interface IBasePresenter<V extends IBaseView>
    Created by Asmar on 01/7/2018.

    Every presenter in the app must either implement this interface or extend BasePresenter indicating the MvpView type that wants to be attached with.
